properties.Name: CommissionScheduleDetailByRevenue
properties.Description: The detail associated with a specific commission schedule when the commission schedule is based on revenue amount.

Columns.Name: CommissionScheduleId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Commission Schedule.

Columns.Name: CommissionMinimumSalesRevenueAmount
Columns.Description: The minimum sales revenue amount for which the associated Commission Schedule is defined or valid.

Columns.Name: CommissionMaximumSalesRevenueAmount
Columns.Description: The maximum sales revenue amount for which the associated Commission Schedule is defined or valid.

Columns.Name: CommissionScheduleDetailStartDate
Columns.Description: The effective start date or first date that the Commission Schedule Detail is in effect.

Columns.Name: CommissionScheduleDetailEndDate
Columns.Description: The effective end date or last date that the Commission Schedule is in effect.

Columns.Name: CommissionBaseAmount
Columns.Description:
The base commission amount paid in accordance with a sale under the Commission Schedule.

This is normally interpreted as a 'minimum base commission amount'.

Columns.Name: CommissionAmountPerUnit
Columns.Description: The amount of the Commission to be paid per unit sold.

Columns.Name: CommissionFlatFeeAmount
Columns.Description:
The flat fee paid as a commission in accordance with a transaction.

This is for cases where the commission is not calculated as a percentage but rather as a flat commission regardless of the number of Product units involved.

Columns.Name: CommissionPercentage
Columns.Description: The percentage of the Commissionable Amount to be paid per product sale.

Columns.Name: CommissionMinimumAmount
Columns.Description: The minimum commission amount charged in conjunction with the Commission Schedule.

Columns.Name: CommissionMaximumAmount
Columns.Description: The maximum commission amount charged in conjunction with the Commission Schedule.

Columns.Name: CommissionScheduleDetailNote
Columns.Description: Notes, comments or additional information regarding the Commission Schedule Detail.

Properties.Description: The detail associated with a specific commission schedule when the commission schedule is based on revenue amount.
